edu.xtec.jclic.automation

Interface ActiveBagContentKit.Compatible

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComplexAssociation, CrossWord, DoublePuzzle, ExchangePuzzle, Explore, HolePuzzle, Identify, InformationScreen, MemoryGame, SimpleAssociation, WordSearch, WrittenAnswer
    Enclosing class:
    ActiveBagContentKit

    public static interface ActiveBagContentKit.Compatible
    Activities should implement this interface when its contents are formed basically by edu.xtec.jclic.bags.ActiveBagContent objects, in order to let AutoContentProvider objects to check whether they are compatible with them.
